                    <span>I bought this book in an effort to learn more about my least favorite NBA franchise--the Los Angeles Lakers.  Unfortunately, the five dysfunctions of the title are not the starting five for the NBA runner-ups.  Instead, it's some kind of business leadership book and pretty good, actually.  I replaced the cover with a picture of a smiling Kobe Bryant and placed it prominently on my bookshelf next to my favorite James Carlos Blake novel.  Another fine mistake.    </span>
                  
              
